#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.60"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.60:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.60:0.2"
msgid "6. Gotamīvagga"
msgstr "6. Gotamī"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an8.60:0.3"
msgid "60. Dutiyapuggalasutta"
msgstr "60. Eight People (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.293"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.60:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhime, bhikkhave, puggalā āhuneyyā … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these eight people are worthy of offerings dedicated to the "
"gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious donation, worthy of "
"greeting with joined palms, and are the supreme field of merit for the world."

msgctxt "an8.60:1.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.60:1.3"
msgid ""
"Sotāpanno, sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyāya paṭipanno … pe … arahā, arahattāya "
"paṭipanno."
msgstr ""
"The stream-enterer and the one practicing to realize the fruit of stream-"
"entry. The once-returner and the one practicing to realize the fruit of once-"
"return. The non-returner and the one practicing to realize the fruit of non-"
"return. The perfected one, and the one practicing for perfection."

msgctxt "an8.60:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ime kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭha puggalā āhuneyyā … pe … anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ "
"lokassāti."
msgstr ""
"These are the eight people who are worthy of offerings dedicated to the "
"gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious donation, worthy of "
"greeting with joined palms, and are the supreme field of merit for the world."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.60:2.1"
msgid "Cattāro ca paṭipannā,"
msgstr "Four practicing the path,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:2.2"
msgid "cattāro ca phale ṭhitā;"
msgstr "and four established in the fruit."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:2.3"
msgid "Esa saṅgho samukkaṭṭho,"
msgstr "This is the exalted Saṅgha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:2.4"
msgid "sattānaṃ aṭṭha puggalā."
msgstr "the eight people among sentient beings."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.60:3.1"
msgid "Yajamānānaṃ manussānaṃ,"
msgstr "For humans, those merit-seeking creatures,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:3.2"
msgid "puññapekkhāna pāṇinaṃ;"
msgstr "who sponsor sacrifices,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:3.3"
msgid "Karotaṃ opadhikaṃ puññaṃ,"
msgstr "making merit with attachments,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:3.4"
msgid "ettha dinnaṃ mahapphalan”ti."
msgstr "what’s given here is very fruitful.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.60:3.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.60:3.6"
msgid "Gotamīvaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.60:4.1"
msgid "Gotamī ovādaṃ saṅkhittaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:4.2"
msgid "dīghajāṇu ca ujjayo;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:4.3"
msgid "Bhayā dve āhuneyyā ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.60:4.4"
msgid "dve ca aṭṭha puggalāti."
msgstr ""
